show.description: When the world underestimates your potential, that's when true transformation begins. This is the thrilling journey of an ordinary man who rewrites his own destiny, caught in a gripping conflict between vengeance and the pursuit of wealth. This story will ignite the fighting spirit within you — not just to win the game, but to redefine it.
